    <p>Here's what 80 grams of protein looks like in a day — and more importantly, here's what it's doing to your muscle while you eat it.</p>

    <p>This post isn't about shaming a number. It's about making the gap visible. Most men eating 80g per day have no idea they're short. The meals look reasonable. Nothing feels wrong. That's exactly the problem — the deficit is silent until the consequences aren't.</p>

